// placing repeater based on direction 
if(DIRECTION == "N"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:1);
elseif(DIRECTION == "E"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:2);
elseif(DIRECTION == "S"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:3);
elseif(DIRECTION == "W"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:0);
endif;
// wait at end of if 
UNSET(@done); log(waiting for done); DO; WAIT(20ms); UNTIL(@done); log(Done!);

endif;

if(DIRECTION == "N"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:1);
elseif(DIRECTION == "E"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:2);
elseif(DIRECTION == "S"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:3);
elseif(DIRECTION == "W"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:0);
endif;
// wait at end of if 
UNSET(@done); log(waiting for done); DO; WAIT(20ms); UNTIL(@done); log(Done!); 
echo(//expand 15 l);
echo(//stack 2 r -s);
UNSET(@done); log(waiting for done); DO; WAIT(20ms); UNTIL(@done); log(Done!); 
echo(//contract 15 r);
echo(//shift 3 r);
echo(//expand 65 l);
echo(//replace air redstone);

echo(//shift 1 d);
// endwire

endif;

elseif(DIRECTION == "E"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:0);
elseif(DIRECTION == "S"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:1);
elseif(DIRECTION == "W"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:2);
endif;
// wait at end of if 
UNSET(@done); log(waiting for done); DO; WAIT(20ms); UNTIL(@done); log(Done!); 
echo(//shift 1 l);
echo(//expand 16 r);
echo(//replace air redstone);
UNSET(@done); log(waiting for done); DO; WAIT(20ms); UNTIL(@done); log(Done!); 
echo(//contract 16 l);
echo(//shift 1 d);
// endwire 
echo(//shift 2 f);
echo(//shift 16 r);
echo(//shift 2 d);
echo(//shift 26 b);
// wire

echo(//shift 1 u);
echo(//shift 14 b);
// placing repeater based on direction 
if(DIRECTION == "N"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:2);
elseif(DIRECTION == "E"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:3);
elseif(DIRECTION == "S"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:0);
elseif(DIRECTION == "W"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:1);
endif;
// wait at end of if 
UNSET(@done); log(waiting for done); DO; WAIT(20ms); UNTIL(@done); log(Done!); 
echo(//shift 16 b);
// placing repeater based on direction 
if(DIRECTION == "N"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:2);

elseif(DIRECTION == "S"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:0);
elseif(DIRECTION == "W"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:1);
endif;

echo(//expand 15 f);
echo(//stack 4 b -s);
UNSET(@done); log(waiting for done); DO; WAIT(20ms); UNTIL(@done); log(Done!); 
echo(//contract 15 b);

echo(//expand 97 f);
echo(//replace air redstone);

echo(//shift 1 d);
// endwire 
echo(//shift 2 r);
echo(//shift 97 f);
// wire

endif;

if(DIRECTION == "N"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:2);
elseif(DIRECTION == "E"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:3);
elseif(DIRECTION == "S"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:0);
elseif(DIRECTION == "W"); echo(//set redstone_repeater:1);
endif;
// wait at end of if 
UNSET(@done); log(waiting for done); DO; WAIT(20ms); UNTIL(@done); log(Done!); 
echo(//expand 15 f);
echo(//stack 4 b -s);
UNSET(@done); log(waiting for done); DO; WAIT(20ms); UNTIL(@done); log(Done!); 
echo(//contract 15 b);
echo(//shift 4 b);
echo(//expand 97 f);
echo(//replace air redstone);
UNSET(@done); log(waiting for done); DO; WAIT(20ms); UNTIL(@done); log(Done!); 
echo(//contract 97 b);
echo(//shift 1 d);
// endwire 
echo(//shift 2 r);
echo(//shift 97 f);
// wire 
echo(//set wool:14);
